<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Nördlingen</head><p>Der Rat teilt die Ordnung der Nürnberger Apotheker mit.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_15" id="7r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_15_r2l1"><expan>Nördling<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_15_r2l2"><expan>Lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnde / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt vnd begert / daʒ vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_15_r2l3">ew <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / was ordnung die <expan>Apotek<ex>er</ex></expan> beÿ vns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Alſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_15_line_1574152768562_83"><expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ewr frewntſchaft wiſſen / daʒ die <expan>Apotek<ex>er</ex></expan> bey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_15_r2l6">vns ſwern / daʒ ſie armen vnd reichen mit fleiʒʒe vnd <expan>gancʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_15_r2l9">trewen machen was Jn <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> empfolhen werd / vnd ob ein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_15_r2l12"><expan>Apotek<ex>er</ex></expan> des das Jm beuolhen <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> würd nicht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_15_r2l15">alles het ſo ſol er das <expan>bringe<ex>n</ex></expan> an den / der Jm das <expan>empholhe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_15_r2l20">hat vnd vmb daſſelb ſol er <expan>neme<ex>n</ex></expan> ſolıch gelt / daʒ er <expan>cʒeitlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_15_line_1574152957628_142">vnd <expan>beſcheidenlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gewin hab / Darnach vviſʒ ſıch ewr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_15_line_1574153025659_188">weiſheit cʒe richten / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> vt <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_15" id="7r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Nördling<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnde, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt und begert, daz
                        wir ew <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, was ordnung die
                                <expan>apotek<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Also <expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                        ewr frewntschaft wissen, daz die <expan>apotek<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns
                        swern, daz sie armen und reichen mit fleizze und
                            <expan>gancze<ex>n</ex></expan> trewen machen, was in
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> empfolhen werd; und ob ein
                                <expan>apotek<ex>er</ex></expan> des das im bevolhen
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> würd nicht alles het, so sol er das
                                <expan>bringe<ex>n</ex></expan> an den, der im das
                                <expan>empholhe<ex>n</ex></expan> hat, und umb dasselb sol er
                                <expan>neme<ex>n</ex></expan> solich gelt, daz er
                                <expan>czeitlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                <expan>bescheidenlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gewin hab. Darnach wisz
                        sich ewr weisheit cze richten. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
